[assistant] - `tests/src/org.liquibase/liquibase-core/4.17.0/src/test/java/org_liquibase/liquibase_core/StartH2CommandStepTest.java`
[assistant] 
[assistant] What it covers:
[assistant] - Executes the public Liquibase `init startH2` command path via `CommandScope`.
[assistant] - Starts H2 TCP and web consoles on available local ports.
[assistant] - Waits until the command reaches the web-session creation/output path.
[assistant] - Verifies TCP database connectivity through JDBC.
[assistant] - Exercises the browser-launch path by setting `launchBrowser` to `true`.
[assistant] - Cleans up the H2 TCP and web servers and restores modified system/user-home state.
[assistant] 
